\mt2 God Me Mame Mina:  
\li1 \k 1. Mamunwa God me mamaib: \k* \xt Mak 10:27; Mak 12:29-30; Ruk 1:37; Ruk 6:35-36; Jon 4:23-24; Apa 14:14-17; Apa 17:22-31; Rom 1:18-23; Rom 11:33-36; 1Ko 8:4-6; 2Ko 1:3; 1Ti 1:17; 1Ti 6:15-16; Ibr 4:13; Ibr 10:30-31; Jms 1:17; 1Pi 1:14-17; 1Jn 1:5; 1Jn 4:7-12,16; Jud 24-25; Rev 4:8-11; Rev 15:3-4\xt*  
\li1 \k 2. God Usiwa, Iesu Keriso, me mamaib: \k*  
\li2 \k Iesu Keriso me God Usiwa. \k* \xt Mat 11:27-30; Mat 16:13-17; Ruk 1:35; Jon 1:1-18; Jon 5:19-29; Jon 6:35-40; Jon 8:58; Jon 11:25-27; Jon 14:5-11; Jon 17:1-5; Jon 20:26-31; Apa 3:13-16; Apa 4:10-12; Rom 1:3-4; 1Ko 3:11; 2Ko 4:4-6; 2Ko 5:21; Gar 4:4-5; Pir 2:5-11; Kor 1:15-20; Kor 2:9-10; Ibr 1:1-14; Ibr 7:26-28; 1Jn 2:1-2; 1Jn 5:20; Rev 1:12-18; Rev 19:11-16\xt*  
\li2 \k God Usiwa apanwan ane, me yaine. \k* \xt Mat 1:18-25; Mat 2:1-23; Ruk 1:26-38; Ruk 2:1-20; Jon 1:14; Gar 4:4-5; Pir 2:6-7; Ibr 2:14-18\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu iyayapan toyau munne, sira yuwat igiyawa warinamunne. \k* \xt Mat 4:23-25; Mat 7:28-29; Mat 9:35-36; Mat 11:1-6; Ruk 4:14-44; Jon 20:30-31; Apa 10:36-38\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu irayauyau obiren ane. \k* \xt Mat 8:1-15,23-33; Mat 9:1-7,18-33; Mat 12:9-14,22; Mat 14:15-32; Mat 15:22-28,32-38; Mat 17:14-18; Mat 20:29-34; Mat 21:18-22; Mak 1:21-28; Mak 7:32-37; Mak 8:22-25; Ruk 5:4-8; Ruk 7:11-15; Ruk 13:10-13; Ruk 14:1-4; Ruk 17:12-14; Ruk 22:50-51; Jon 2:1-11; Jon 4:46-54; Jon 5:5-9; Jon 9:1-7; Jon 11:11-44; Jon 21:4-6; Apa 2:22\xt*  
\li2 \k Namuyoiyoi igiyawa Iesu yumiya, sira Iesu tope boatan oya waya. \k* \xt Mat 26:47-68; Mat 27:1-2,11-31; Mak 14:43-65; Mak 15:1-20; Ruk 22:47-53; Ruk 22:63–23:25; Jon 18:1-14,19-24; Jon 18:28–19:16\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu korosi gumbe toya boane. \k* \xt Mat 27:32-56; Mak 15:21-41; Ruk 23:26-49; Jon 19:17-37\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu dagup danave barauya. \k* \xt Mat 27:57-66; Mak 15:42-47; Ruk 23:50-56; Jon 19:38-42\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu sira inaig yoine, iyayapan me yauya. \k* \xt Mat 28:1-20; Mak 16:1-8; Ruk 24:1-49; Jon 20:1–21:14; Apa 1:3-8; Apa 2:24-32; Apa 3:15; Apa 4:10,33; Apa 10:39-43; Apa 13:29-39; Apa 17:2-3,30-31; Rom 1:4; Rom 4:24-25; 1Ko 15:3-8,12-21; Rev 1:18\xt*  
\li2 \k Iesu sira taig kwimin dog aine. \k* \xt Ruk 24:50-51; Apa 1:9-11; Apa 2:32-36; Apa 5:30-31; Rom 8:34; Epe 1:20-23; Pir 2:9-11; Ibr 1:3-11; Ibr 2:9; Ibr 4:14-16; Ibr 7:25-26; Ibr 10:12-14; 1Pi 3:22\xt*  
\li1 \k 3. Guwawa Iyakaisiyapama me mamaib. \k* \xt Mat 28:19; Mak 1:9-11; Mak 3:28-30; Ruk 1:35; Ruk 3:16; Ruk 4:1; Ruk 11:13; Ruk 12:12; Jon 1:32-34; Jon 3:5-8; Jon 7:37-39; Jon 14:15-17,26; Jon 15:26; Jon 16:7-15; Jon 20:19-23; Apa 1:4-5,8; Apa 2:1-18,38-39; Apa 4:31; Apa 5:3-5; Apa 8:14-17; Apa 10:44-48; Apa 13:2-4; Apa 15:28; Apa 16:7-10; Apa 19:1-7; Rom 5:5; Rom 7:6; Rom 8:9-16,26-27; 1Ko 2:4,9-16; 1Ko 3:16; 1Ko 6:11,19; 1Ko 12:1-13; 2Ko 1:21-22; 2Ko 5:5; 2Ko 13:14; Gar 3:2-5; Gar 4:6; Gar 5:16-18,22-25; Epe 1:13-14,17; Epe 3:16; Epe 4:3-4,30; Epe 5:18-20; Epe 6:17-18; 1Te 1:5-6; 1Te 5:19; 2Te 2:13; Tai 3:5-6; Ibr 2:4; Ibr 9:14; 1Pi 1:2,11; 2Pi 1:20-21; 1Jn 2:20; 1Jn 3:24; 1Jn 4:13; 1Jn 5:6-8\xt*  
\li1 \k 4. God dividivi undag wadne. \k* \xt Mat 19:4; Jon 1:3; Apa 14:15; Apa 17:24-26; 1Ko 8:6; Kor 1:15-16; Ibr 1:2; Ibr 11:3; Rev 4:11\xt*  
\li1 \k 5. God dividivi undag amaraivi. \k* \xt Mat 6:25-34; Mat 10:29-31; Apa 14:15-17; Rom 8:28; 11:36; Kor 1:17; Ibr 1:3; Jms 4:13-16\xt*  
\s1 Iyayapan mu mamaib.  
\li1 \k 6. Iyayapan undag kukaeba aya. \k* \xt Jon 8:7-9; Rom 3:9-20,23; Rom 5:12; Gar 3:22; 1Jn 1:8-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 7. Iyayapan kukaeba apewa, mu mamaib: \k* \xt Rom 1:18-32; Rom 8:5-8; Gar 5:19-21; Epe 2:1-3; Epe 5:3-5; Kor 3:5-10; Jms 4:17; 1Pi 4:3; 1Jn 3:4-5\xt*  
\li1 \k 8. Iyayapan kukaeba muma oya ibnawa wakene, meoya mu waita autan anoeme. \k* \xt Mat 10:28; Mat 13:41-42; Jon 3:18-20,36; Apa 17:30-31; Rom 1:18-19; Rom 6:23; Gar 6:7-8; Kor 3:5-6; 2Te 1:7-9; Ibr 9:27; Ibr 10:26-31; 1Pi 1:17; 1Pi 4:3-5; Jud 7; Rev 20:11-15\xt*  
\s1 Mame Mina God Iyayapan Gumbo Waita Mumpe Kukaeba Muma Oya:  
\li1 \k 9. God iyayapan undag baigan munivi, sira waita muntan anoivi. \k* \xt Jon 3:16; Rom 5:8; 1Ti 2:3-6; 2Pi 3:9; 1Jn 4:9-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 10. God Usiwa, Iesu Keriso, botone waita nuntan oya. \k* \xt Mak 10:45; Jon 3:16; Rom 4:25; Rom 5:8; 1Ko 15:3-4; 2Ko 5:19-21; Gar 3:13; 1Ti 2:5-6; Ibr 2:9; Ibr 9:28; 1Pi 1:18-20; 1Pi 2:24-25; 1Pi 3:18; 1Jn 2:2; Rev 5:8-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 11. Iesu bo meuma kukaeba numawa atan aune. \k* \xt Mat 26:26-29; Rom 3:25; Rom 5:9-10; Epe 1:7; Ibr 9:11-14; 1Jn 1:6-7; Rev 7:14-17\xt*  
\li1 \k 12. God kukaeba anog yankwene. \k* \xt Apa 5:31; Apa 10:43; Apa 26:18; Epe 1:7; Epe 4:32; Kor 1:13-14; Kor 2:13-14; Ibr 10:17-18; 1Jn 1:8-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 13. God ane nu oraivitwa God yangave. \k* \xt Apa 13:38-39; Rom 1:16-17; Rom 3:21-26; Rom 5:1,18-19; Gar 2:16; Gar 3:6-9; Tai 3:7\xt*  
\li1 \k 14. God inaiinai mataiwa nunne. \k* \xt Jon 3:1-16; Jon 5:19-29; Jon 10:10; Jon 11:25-26; Jon 14:6; Jon 17:2-3; Jon 20:31; Rom 5:21; Rom 6:5-14; Rom 8:10-17; 2Ko 5:17; Gar 2:20; Epe 2:1-6; Kor 2:13; Kor 3:1-4; 2Ti 1:10; Tai 3:4-7; 1Pi 1:23; 1Jn 5:11-13\xt*  
\li1 \k 15. God ane nu God usitainawa atu. \k* \xt Jon 1:12-13; Rom 8:14-17; Gar 4:6-7; Ibr 12:5-11; 1Jn 3:1-3\xt*  
\s1 God Waita Nuntan Anoivi. Nu Me Yaug Anotawa, Divi Aton?  
\li1 \k 16. Kukaeba atu oya danadawai auete, meoya kukaeba den aigimta. \k* \xt Mat 4:17;; Mak 6:12; Ruk 13:1-5; Ruk 15:1-31; Ruk 24:45-47; Apa 2:37-40; Apa 3:19-20; Apa 17:29-31; Apa 20:21; Apa 26:19-20; 2Ko 7:8-11; 2Pi 3:9; Rev 9:20-21\xt*  
\li1 \k 17. Nu anotumat ete Iesu waita numpe. \k* \xt Jon 1:12; Jon 3:15-18,36; Jon 6:47; Jon 14:6; Jon 20:31; Apa 4:12; Apa 16:30-31; Rom 3:20-22; Rom 10:9-10; Gar 2:16; Epe 2:8-9\xt*  
\li1 \k 18. God yaug anotan oya sira nu dimbae aton God anoiviwa yaug anotan oya nu Baiboru basiaigimta. \k* \xt Mat 4:1-4; Mat 5:17-20; Mat 22:29; Jon 8:31-32; Jon 20:31; Apa 20:32; Rom 15:4; Rom 16:26; Kor 3:16; 1Te 2:13; 1Ti 4:13; 2Ti 3:14-17; Ibr 4:12; 1Pi 1:22-25; 2Pi 1:19-21; 2Jn 9-10; Rev 1:3\xt*  
\li1 \k 19. Nu babataito atu. \k* \xt Mat 28:18-20; Jon 3:22; Jon 4:1-2; Apa 2:37-42; Apa 8:12,36-38; Apa 10:44-48; Apa 16:14-15,31-33; Apa 19:1-7; Apa 22:12-16; Rom 6:1-4; Gar 3:26-27; Kor 2:12; 1Pi 3:20-22\xt*  
\li1 \k 20. Nu anotumat igiyawa upeba gaibu agoniyatu. \k* \xt Mat 18:19-20; Apa 2:41-47; Rom 12:4-8; Epe 1:22-23; Epe 4:11-16; Kor 3:15-17; 1Ti 4:13; Ibr 10:24-25\xt*  
\li1 \k 21. Nu anotumat igiyawa upeba gaibu toborag Ayapan Augoi Nakwaeba naigimta. \k* \xt Mat 26:26-30; Mak 14:22-26; Ruk 22:14-20; 1Ko 10:14-22; 1Ko 11:17-34\xt*  
\s1 Nu Iesu Keriso Gumbe Anotumat Ete Igiyawa. Nu Mamaib Wakeigimta:  
\li1 \k 22. Nu God, Mamunwa God, Iesu Keriso, Ayapan numa, noiwa avigimta. \k* \xt Jon 14:15,21,23-24; Jon 15:10-17; Rom 13:8-10; 1Pi 1:14-16; 1Jn 2:3-8; 1Jn 3:22-24; 2Jn 5-6\xt*  
\li1 \k 23. Nu God ge iyayapan numawa baigan munta. \k* \xt Mat 22:34-40; Mak 12:28-34; Ruk 10:25-37; Jon 14:21; Mat 5:43-48; Jon 13:34-35; Jon 15:12-17; Rom 12:9-10; Rom 13:8-10; 1Ko 13:1-3; 1Ko 16:14; Gar 5:13-15; 1Te 4:9-10; 1Pi 1:8; 1Pi 4:8; 1Jn 2:9-11; 1Jn 3:11-18; 1Jn 4:7-21; 1Jn 5:3\xt*  
\li1 \k 24. Keriso mina nu meib aigimta. \k* \xt Jon 13:34-35; Jon 14:27; Rom 12:9-13; Gar 5:22-26; Kor 3:12-17; 1Te 5:16-18\xt*  
\li1 \k 25. Nun waigimta. \k*  
\li2 \k Nun aninin waton? \k* \xt Mat 6:5-13; Mat 7:7-11; Mat 18:19-20; Mak 11:24-25; Ruk 11:1-13; Ruk 18:1-8; Ruk 21:36; Jon 14:13-14; Jon 15:7; Jon 16:23-26; Rom 8:26-27; Rom 12:12; Epe 2:18; Epe 6:18; Pir 4:6-7; Kor 4:2; 1Te 5:17; 1Ti 2:1-4,8; 1Ti 4:4-5; Ibr 4:16; Ibr 10:19-22; Jms 1:5-8; Jms 4:2-3; Jms 5:13-18; 1Pi 4:7; 1Jn 3:21-22; 1Jn 5:14-15\xt*  
\li2 \k Iyayapan aninin nun vemewa gwagwawa mamaib: \k* \xt Mat 11:25-26; Mat 14:23; Mat 19:13-15; Mak 1:35; Ruk 5:16; Ruk 6:12; Ruk 22:32,39-46; Jon 11:41-42; Jon 17:1-26; Apa 4:24-31; Apa 16:25; Apa 20:36; Apa 21:5; Rom 1:9-10; Rom 10:1-2; Rom 15:30-33; 2Ko 12:7-10; Epe 1:15-20; Epe 3:14-21; Epe 6:19-20; Pir 1:3-5,9-11; Kor 1:9-12; Kor 4:3-4; 1Te 3:9-13; 2Te 1:11-12; 2Te 3:1-5; Ibr 5:7; Ibr 7:25\xt*  
\li1 \k 26. Nu evedni God gumbe gaun wanigimta. \k* \xt Ruk 17:11-19; Jon 6:11; Rom 1:21; Epe 5:20; Pir 4:4-7; Kor 2:7; Kor 3:17; Kor 4:2; 1Te 5:18; 1Ti 2:1; 1Ti 4:4-5\xt*  
\li1 \k 27. Nu iyayapan upeba waita munigimta. \k* \xt Mat 6:1-4; Mat 7:12; Mat 25:31-46; Ruk 3:10-11; Ruk 6:38; Apa 11:27-30; 1Ko 10:24; 2Ko 8:1-15; 2Ko 9:1-15; Gar 6:9-10; Pir 4:14-19; Ibr 10:24; Ibr 13:1-3,16; Jms 1:27; Jms 2:15-16; 1Jn 3:16-18\xt*  
\li1 \k 28. Nu mokona aigimta. \k* \xt Mat 5:3-12; Mat 18:1-5; Ruk 14:7-11; Ruk 18:9-14; Epe 4:2; Pir 2:3-11; Kor 3:12-13; Jms 4:5-10; 1Pi 5:5-7\xt*  
\li1 \k 29. Nu anmaga ge tawara upeba oya mamaib anoete: \k* \xt Mat 6:19-21,24-34; Ruk 12:13-21,32-34; Apa 20:35; 1Ti 6:6-10,17-19; Ibr 13:5-6; Jms 2:1-9; Jms 5:1-6\xt*  
\li1 \k 30. Oma ape ipewa, nu puyuyu atanwa topai anoete. \k* \xt Mat 5:25-26,38-42; Mat 18:15-17; Rom 12:14-21; 1Ko 6:1-8\xt*  
\li1 \k 31. Amareme igiyawa ayamat amunigimta. \k* \xt Mat 22:15-22; Apa 5:27-29; Rom 13:1-7; 1Ti 2:1-4; Tai 3:1; 1Pi 2:13-17\xt*  
\li1 \k 32. God ugaugaeba den waiyata. \k* \xt Mat 4:10; Apa 17:22-31; 1Ko 5:11; 1Ko 6:9-11; 1Ko 8:1-13; 1Ko 10:1-22; 2Ko 6:14-18; Gar 5:19-21; 1Te 1:9-10; 1Jn 5:21; Rev 21:8; Rev 22:15\xt*  
\li1 \k 33. Kwasisim den ata. \k* \xt Apa 13:4-12; Apa 19:11-20; Gar 5:19-21; Rev 21:8; Rev 22:15\xt*  
\li1 \k 34. Mae puyowawa den okerigimta. \k* \xt Mat 9:13; Mak 12:33; Rom 12:1; Ibr 9:6–10:18\xt*  
\li1 \k 35. Uinantaraki den ata. \k* \xt Mat 5:27-30; Jon 8:2-11; Rom 13:8-10; 1Ko 5:9-11; 1Ko 6:9-20; Gar 5:19; Epe 5:3; Kor 3:5-6; 1Te 4:1-8; Ibr 13:4; Jud 7\xt*  
\li1 \k 36. Yoi yusipama den nag nokonoko aigimta. \k* \xt Rom 13:13; 1Ko 5:11; 1Ko 6:9-11; Gar 5:19-21; Epe 5:18; 1Ti 3:1-3; Tai 1:7; 1Pi 4:3-5\xt*  
\s1 Siosi Me Mamaib:  
\li1 \k 37. Siosi igiyawa mu mamaib: \k* \xt Mat 16:13-20; Apa 2:41-42; Rom 12:4-8; 1Ko 12:12-30; Epe 1:22-23; Epe 2:19-22; Epe 4:1-16; Kor 1:18; Ibr 10:24-25; 1Pi 2:4-10; Rev 19:5-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 38. Siosi amareme igiyawa mu mamaib: \k* \xt Apa 6:1-6; Apa 14:23; 1Ti 3:1-13; Tai 1:5-9\xt*  
\li1 \k 39. Siosi amareme igiyawa mu mamaib waketanit di: \k* \xt Mat 28:18-20; Ruk 22:24-27; Apa 20:17-35; 1Te 2:1-12; 1Ti 4:1-16; 2Ti 2:1-26; 2Ti 3:10–4:5; Tai 2:7-8; 1Pi 5:1-4\xt*  
\li1 \k 40. Siosi amareme igiyawa ayamat amunta. \k* \xt 1Ko 9:14; Gar 6:6; 1Te 5:12-13; 1Ti 5:17-22; Ibr 13:7,17\xt*  
\s1 Inamamawa Ge Ututainapam Me Mamaib:  
\li1 \k 41. Memabivi mu mamaib: \k* \xt Mat 19:4-6; 1Ko 7:1-16; Epe 5:21-33; Kor 3:18-19; Tai 2:3-5; Ibr 13:4; 1Pi 3:1-7\xt*  
\li1 \k 42. Usitainawa mu mamaib: \k* \xt Mat 15:3-6; Ruk 2:51; Epe 6:1-3; Kor 3:20; 1Ti 5:4,8; Ibr 12:7-11\xt*  
\li1 \k 43. Inamamawa mu mamaib: \k* \xt Epe 6:4; Kor 3:21; 1Ti 3:4-5\xt*  
\li1 \k 44. Kwapura mu mamaib: \k* \xt Apa 6:1; Rom 7:2-3; 1Ko 7:39-40; 1Ti 5:3-16; Jms 1:27\xt*  
\li1 \k 45. Garakue den ata. \k* \xt Mat 5:31-32; Mat 19:3-9; Ruk 16:18; Rom 7:2-3; 1Ko 7:10-16\xt*  
\s1 Anotumat Igiyawa Kum Dada Ano Gwambe Ete.  
\li1 \k 46. Mu yaug anotanit di ibnawa aupewa. \k* \xt Rom 8:18-25,28; 2Ko 1:4; 2Ko 4:16-18; Jms 1:2-4; 1Pi 1:6-9; 1Pi 2:19-21; 1Pi 5:8-10\xt*  
\li1 \k 47. Mu yaug anotanit di edawai uwamumpewa. \k* \xt Mat 5:10-12; Mak 13:9-13; Ruk 12:4-9; Jon 15:18-21; Jon 16:1-4; Apa 5:41; Rom 8:35-37; Rom 12:12-14,17-21; 1Ko 4:11-13; 2Ko 4:8-11; 2Ko 12:10; Pir 1:28-29; 2Te 1:4-8; 2Te 3:2-4; 2Ti 3:10-13; Ibr 10:32-39; Ibr 12:3-4; 1Pi 3:13-17; 1Pi 4:12-19; Rev 2:10\xt*  
\li1 \k 48. Boaeba mu den eme. \k* \xt Jon 6:39-40; Jon 11:17-27; Jon 14:1-4; Rom 8:10-11,38-39; Rom 14:7-9; 1Ko 15:12-58; 2Ko 5:1-10; Pir 1:20-24; 1Te 4:13-18; Ibr 2:14-15; Rev 14:13; Rev 21:1-4; Rev 22:1-5\xt*  
\li1 \k 49. God mu gombo sira waita munivi. \k* \xt Mat 18:19-20; Mat 28:19-20; Jon 14:16-23; Rom 8:35-39; 2Ko 6:16-18; Epe 3:17-19; Pir 4:13; Kor 2:6-7; 2Te 3:16; Ibr 13:5-6\xt*  
\li1 \k 50. Seitan didimama ag wakukam munivi. \k* \xt Mat 13:19; Ruk 4:1-13; Ruk 22:3-4; Jon 8:42-44; 2Ko 2:10-11; 2Ko 4:4; 2Ko 11:13-15; Epe 2:2; 1Te 2:18; 2Te 2:9-12; 1Pi 5:8-9; 1Jn 3:8-10; Rev 12:7-12; Rev 20:1-3,10\xt*  
\li1 \k 51. God yusiwa mumpe Seitan gumbe mut aigimtan oya sira ibnawa gumbe nikiyag wakeigimtan oya. \k* \xt Mat 4:1-11; Mat 6:13; Ruk 22:31-32; Jon 17:14-19; Rom 8:31-39; Rom 12:12; Rom 16:19-20; 1Ko 10:12-13; 1Ko 16:13; 2Ko 12:7-10; Epe 3:20-21; Epe 6:10-18; Pir 4:13; 1Te 3:5-8; 2Te 3:3; 2Ti 1:7-8; Ibr 2:18; Ibr 4:14-16; Ibr 12:1-2; Jms 4:7; 1Pi 1:5; 1Pi 5:8-11; 1Jn 4:4; 1Jn 5:3-5; Rev 12:7-12\xt*  
\li1 \k 52. God kum evedni yuwat igiyawa warinamunivi. \k* \xt Mat 4:23-25; Mat 9:35; Mat 11:2-5; Apa 3:1-6; Apa 8:4-8; Apa 19:11-16; Apa 28:8-9; 1Ko 12:9,29-30; 2Ko 12:7-10; 1Ti 5:23; 2Ti 4:20; Jms 5:14-15\xt*  
\s1 Kum Ivi Divi Matappe?  
\li1 \k 53. Iesu piyu mame sira taig ompe. \k* \xt Mat 24:29-44; Jon 14:1-3; Apa 1:10-11; Apa 3:19-21; Pir 3:20-21; Kor 3:4; 1Te 1:9-10; 1Te 3:13; 1Te 4:13–5:11; 2Te 1:6-10; 2Te 2:1-4; 1Ti 6:13-15; 2Ti 4:8; Ibr 9:28; 2Pi 3:1-18; 1Jn 3:1-3; Rev 1:7; Rev 22:12-13\xt*  
\li1 \k 54. God iyayapan undag Iesu Keriso gumbe keptete amumpe. \k* \xt Mat 7:21-23; Mat 16:24-27; Mat 25:31-46; Jon 3:18-21; Jon 5:24-29; Apa 17:30-31; Rom 2:1-11; Rom 14:10-12; 1Ko 3:10-15; 1Ko 4:5; 2Ko 5:9-10; 2Te 1:5-10; Ibr 9:27-28; Ibr 10:26-31; 1Pi 1:17; 1Pi 4:3-5; Rev 20:11-15\xt*  
\li1 \k 55. Bira da mu waita auyawa kwimin danave wakeigimpe. \k* \xt Ruk 12:32-34; Jon 14:1-3; 2Ko 5:1-8; Pir 1:23; 1Pi 1:4-5; Rev 4:1-11; Rev 21:1-4; Rev 21:22–22:5; Rev 22:14-15\xt*  
\li1 \k 56. Bira da mu waita den auyawa mu at kukaeba danave wakeigimpe. \k* \xt Mat 10:28; Mat 13:41-42,47-50; Mat 25:41; Ruk 16:23-26; 2Te 1:9; Rev 20:10-15; Rev 21:8\xt*  